  "signal_description": "The query analyzes the automation rate for three different processes: Purchase Order, Invoice, and Payment. For each process, it calculates the ratio of the count of distinct 'Inv. Accounting Document Number' filtered by specific conditions to the total count of 'Inv. Accounting Document Number' filtered by the same conditions. If the automation rate is above 70%, it returns the message 'Automation rate is above 70%. No action needed.' If the automation rate is between 30% and 70%, it returns the message 'Automation rate is between 30% and 70%. Potential for improvement.' If the automation rate is below 30%, it returns the message 'Automation rate is below 30%. Improvement highly recommended.' The analysis is performed on the 'defaultview-225' table."
}
